snippet.title: TRINITY HEART DEMO FINAL TRAILER MAY 20TH
snippet.description:
https://hushed-dreamware.itch.io/trinity-heart-world-1-demo
Trinity Heart Demo available this weekend!

(DISCLAIMER) Not all levels shown in trailer to be playable in demo. This is all purely for representation of the gameplay loop, and appeal. This is the current build of the game and does not represent a finalized product.
